latestPosts.caption:
Photographing @GauravGuptaOfficial’s new bridal campaign, The Vow @GauravGuptaBrides, in India was unforgettable. Each piece bridges heritage with modern identity, inviting brides, grooms, and their families to embrace tradition while redefining it on their own terms. The ivory lehenga, crafted over 900 hours and adorned with 3,000 pearls, 2,000 crystal drops, and glass beads, is a testament to the brand’s extraordinary craftsmanship. From intimate palace pheras to seaside destination weddings, the collection offers a couture language for every kind of celebration. We’ve long admired Gaurav Gupta for how his designs push the boundaries of structure and form, and working closely with his brilliant team only deepened our appreciation and love for his visionary world of couture. This shoot was more than fashion—it was a timeless narrative come to life. 

Photographed by @amritphotography
Assisted by @johnvisuals.co
